</td>
</tr>
</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Say <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloom=
bergbusiness.com/click/25723599.270661/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS9hcnRpY2xl=
cy9vaGlvLXN1ZXMtbWV0YS1hbGxlZ2luZy1mYWNlYm9vay1wYXJlbnQtbWlzbGVkLXB1YmxpYy1=
